/* 花草百科全书 - 首页样式（白色清爽风格） */
/* 参考：白底 + 绿色点缀 + 大植物视觉 */

/* ========== 容器 ========== */
.container {
  min-height: 100vh;
  background: #ffffff;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  padding: 0;
  position: relative;
}

/* ========== 顶部区域：大植物视觉 ========== */
.header-section {
  width: 100%;
  height: 45vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fdf8 0%, #ffffff 100%);
  padding-top: 40rpx;
}

.plant-img {
  width: 70%;
  max-height: 40vh;
}

/* ========== 品牌区域 ========== */
.brand-section {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 30rpx 0 40rpx;
}

.brand-name {
  font-size: 44rpx;
  font-weight: bold;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  margin-bottom: 12rpx;
}

.brand-slogan {
  font-size: 26rpx;
  color: #27ae60;
}

/* ========== 核心功能按钮 ========== */
.action-section {
  padding: 0 40rpx;
}

.main-btn {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  background: #f5f5f5;
  border-radius: 20rpx;
  padding: 28rpx 30rpx;
  margin-bottom: 20rpx;
}

.main-btn.secondary {
  background: #fafafa;
}

.btn-icon-wrap {
  width: 80rpx;
  height: 80rpx;
  background: #27ae60;
  border-radius: 16rpx;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-right: 24rpx;
}

.btn-icon-wrap.light {
  background: #e8f5e9;
}

.btn-icon {
  font-size: 36rpx;
}

.btn-content {
  flex: 1;
}

.btn-title {
  font-size: 30rpx;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  display: block;
}

.btn-desc {
  font-size: 24rpx;
  color: #888;
  margin-top: 4rpx;
  display: block;
}

.btn-arrow {
  font-size: 36rpx;
  color: #ccc;
}

/* ========== 快捷入口 ========== */
.quick-actions {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-around;
  padding: 40rpx 40rpx 30rpx;
}

.quick-item {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
}

.quick-icon {
  font-size: 44rpx;
  margin-bottom: 8rpx;
}

.quick-text {
  font-size: 24rpx;
  color: #666;
}

/* ========== 底部装饰 ========== */
.footer-decor {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 30rpx 0 50rpx;
}

.footer-text {
  font-size: 24rpx;
  color: #bbb;
}